WEBVTT

00:00.520 --> 00:02.360
No one could threaten me before

00:02.800 --> 00:04.000
And never will in the future

00:08.920 --> 00:09.960
In this life

00:10.880 --> 00:12.800
Will only have one wife, the Xie family

00:15.000 --> 00:17.200
April of the 24th year of Xuan

00:17.480 --> 00:20.200
Sikong Yao purged the capital's gentry

00:20.600 --> 00:22.760
Chen Dao, finally arriving, was enraged

00:22.760 --> 00:24.920
Ordered Qingzhou Army to wear white headbands

00:24.920 --> 00:26.240
And fiercely attacked the capital

00:26.480 --> 00:29.280
Soon after, Zu Yue was also drawn into battle

00:29.560 --> 00:32.440
Xuan thus fell into prolonged civil war
